data.description: This is a lovely home with great curb appeal in desirable James Landing. There are numerous upgrades throughout, including the kitchen with new cabinets, appliances, and granite counters, updated bathrooms, and hardwood floors throughout most of the house, including the FROG (5th bedroom). There is a step down living room, a separate den with a wood burning fireplace, formal dining room, and a primary bedroom with 2 closets, including a walk-in closet with an automatic light. All of the bedrooms are spacious and there is also a huge laundry/mud room, and 2 concrete areas in the back perfect for back yard entertaining!
